name: Danger Dingo #05 - Cal, The Mad
description:
Cal is Danger Dingo #05 in the Danger Dingo collection by @CuddleofDeath!

Cal was born in a secret underground facility within the DD universe.

Programmed as an alchemist of the highest caliber, Cal never fails to take risks when it comes to minting up new potions and other alchemical wonders.

There was a story of an individual who was seen getting taken into Cal's laboratory...but they never came back out.

All other information regarding Cal is classified.
